OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FThousands of farmers are expected to
OL,8,Fgather outside the Senedd in in the
OL,9,Fbiggest protest seen so far against
OL,10,Fthe Welsh Government's future subsidy
OL,11,Fplans.
OL,13,FFarmers in Wales have a series of
OL,14,Fgrievances with the Welsh Government
OL,15,Fwhich have reached a crescendo in
OL,16,Frecent weeks, leading to protests and
OL,17,Fthe sight of convoys of tractors.
