OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FMost prominently they're trying to
OL,8,Fpersuade Welsh ministers to change
OL,9,Ftheir minds when it comes to a new
OL,10,Fsystem of subsidies, under which
OL,11,Fthey'd be paid for working to help the
OL,12,Fenvironment rather than simply
OL,13,Fproducing food.
OL,15,FBut they're also angry about the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment's anti-water pollution
OL,17,Fscheme and they're worried that TB in
OL,18,Fcattle continues to be a big problem
OL,19,Fhere in Wales.
