OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FPolitics is complicating the issue.
OL,8,FThe Welsh Government is controlled by
OL,9,FLabour which sees the changes as part
OL,10,Fof tackling a climate change crisis.
OL,12,FConservatives both here and in
OL,13,FWestminster have made it part of their
OL,14,Fclaim to be committed to what they see
OL,15,Fas more sensible steps to tackle
OL,16,Fclimate change.
OL,18,FWhat is the Sustainable Farming Scheme?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
