OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FThe Welsh Government is consulting on
OL,8,Fa system known as the Sustainable
OL,9,FFarming Scheme (SFS) which would be
OL,10,Fintroduced in 2025.
OL,12,FUnlike the EU's Common Agricultural
OL,13,FPolicy scheme, farmers would be
OL,14,Frewarded for providing 'public goods'
OL,15,Ffrom the land, including social and
OL,16,Fenvironmental improvements.
OL,18,FThey wouldn't receive payments for
OL,19,Fproducing food, which the Welsh
OL,20,FGovernment argues, has a market value.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
