OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FEnvironmental groups broadly welcome
OL,8,Fthe SFS proposals but farmers say that
OL,9,Ffood production should also be
OL,10,Feligible for support.
OL,12,FThey're also concerned about a
OL,13,Frequirement to give over some of the
OL,14,Fland - up to 10% - to nature, such as
OL,15,Fby growing trees. They argue that this
OL,16,Fwill put too much of a burden on
OL,17,Ffarmers, cost jobs and reduce food
OL,18,Fproduction.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
