OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FThe Conservatives both here and in
OL,8,FWestminster have joined criticism of
OL,9,Fthe proposals and taken part in
OL,10,Fprotests. Last weekend, Rishi Sunak
OL,11,Fhimself spoke to protesting farmers
OL,12,Fwho'd parked their tractors outside
OL,13,Fthe Welsh Conservative conference. The
OL,14,Fprime minister told them "We've got
OL,15,Fyour backs."
OL,17,FHowever, the UK Government is also
OL,18,Fphasing in a new subsidy scheme which
OL,19,Falso involves switching qualification
OL,20,Ffor payment to rewards.
