OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FThe Environmental Land Management
OL,8,Fscheme proposed for England will
OL,9,Freward farmers, tenants, landowners
OL,10,Fand others for delivering "public
OL,11,Fgoods" and making "a significant
OL,12,Fcontribution to the environment."
OL,14,FThe concerns over Bovine TB
OL,16,FMeanwhile, for many beef and dairy
OL,17,Ffarmers, the biggest complaint has to
OL,18,Fdo with TB in cattle.
