OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FAny showing signs of the disease are
OL,8,Fkilled, with up to 10,000 slaughtered
OL,9,Flast year. Many farmers are calling
OL,10,Ffor a badger cull, similar to that
OL,11,Fwhich takes place in England, but the
OL,12,FWelsh Government has resisted,
OL,13,Fpreferring enhanced testing.
OL,15,FIn a written statement, Mark Drakeford
OL,16,Fand Lesley Griffiths MS, Minister for
OL,17,FRural Affairs, North Wales and
OL,18,FTrefnydd said they recognised the
OL,19,F"devastation a TB breakdown brings to
OL,20,Fa farming family and business."
