OL,7,FThey added that they were committed to
OL,8,Fexploring other approaches to on-farm
OL,9,Fslaughter and are appointing a Bovine
OL,10,FTB Technical Advisory Group.
OL,12,FWater pollution regulations
OL,14,FAnother Welsh Government environmental
OL,15,Fpolicy is causing concern to farmers:
OL,16,Fthe effort to prevent water pollution.
