OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FNitrate Vulnerable Zones (NVZs) are
OL,8,Fdesigned to control the overuse of
OL,9,Fnitrates which are found in
OL,10,Ffertilisers, manure and slurry and can
OL,11,Ffind their way from fields into lakes
OL,12,Fand rivers, harming wildlife and can
OL,13,Fend up in drinking water.
OL,15,FPreviously a very small amount (2-4%)
OL,16,Fof the land was designated as NVZs
OL,17,Fmeaning that farmers within those
OL,18,Fzones were subject to controls.
