OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cprotesting outside the Senedd in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FHowever, since 2021, there have been
OL,8,Fnew all-Wales regulations to tackle
OL,9,Fthe causes of agricultural pollution.
OL,10,FThe farming unions have called the
OL,11,Frules "draconian" and a sledgehammer
OL,12,Fto crack a nut. Environmental
OL,13,Fcampaigners say it creates a level
OL,14,Fplaying field for all farmers.
OL,16,FIn a written statement published on
OL,17,FTuesday, the Welsh Government said:
OL,18,F"Regulations are needed to protect the
OL,19,Fenvironment from poor practice, which
OL,20,Fis causing considerable damage to the
OL,21,Freputation of the sector."
