OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FThe statement added that #20m of
OL,8,Fadditional funding will be made
OL,9,Favailable to help farmers comply with
OL,10,Fthe requirements and that a new round
OL,11,Fof the Nutrient Management Investment
OL,12,FScheme will be launched shortly.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government has said that
OL,15,Farrangements have been put in place
OL,16,Ffor the first statutory review of the
OL,17,Feffectiveness of the regulations and
OL,18,Fthat it will consult on the
OL,19,Fsuitability of the alternative
OL,20,Fmeasures proposals received from the
OL,21,Fsector.
